node.text:
“Dear Mama was written for me, yes, but like all things with Tupac, it was also written for other mothers…It was written for Malcolm X’s wife, Betty Shabazz.  It was written for Coretta Scott King…It was written for Mothers in that situation…It was written for mother’s with sons, you know, struggling to do the best that they can”
-Afeni Shakur

Link in bio to watch the “Dear Mama” music video
